name: E X O D U S

metadata.name: #case 01 "Casey Reynolds"
metadata.description:
"Just a few minutes ago, she was relaxing on the balcony of her villa..."  
  
She was supposed to be taking a vacation to refresh her body and soul at the villa on a green mountainside, but she was just running through the dark forest...  
  
No pursuers.  
After regaining some composure, she stops and begins to sort out the situation.  
  
"I think... while sipping a cup of tea and looking endlessly at social networking sites... she saw... something... she can't remember  ......."  
  
When I came to, I was lying in the woods.  
The strange noises I heard as I moved my body made me feel uncomfortable, almost like fear.  
  
The fact that she felt physically fit despite this unusual situation, on the contrary, made her anxious...  
  
「(ついさっきまで、別荘のバルコニーでくつろいでいたはず…)」  
  
緑深い山の中腹にある別荘で、心身共にリフレッシュする為休暇を取っていたはずの彼女は、ただ暗い森を駆けていた…  
  
追手はない。  
少しだけ落ち着きを取り戻した彼女は、立ち止まり、状況を整理し始める。  
  
「たしか…紅茶を飲みながら、SNSを延々と眺めていたら…何かを見た…気がする……思い出せない。」  
  
気が付いた時には、森の中に横たわっていた。  
身体を動かすと聞こえる異音に、恐怖にも似た違和感を覚えた。  
  
この異常事態にもかかわらず体調が万全に感じる事が、逆に彼女の不安を煽った…
